# Examples:
* Basic Commands


* Concept of Pipes
ls | cowsay
fortune | cowsay
fortune | cowsay > thecow.txt

* Generate 100 Directories, with a for loop
for i in 1 2 3 4 5
do
   echo "Welcome $i times"
done

for i in {1..100}
do 
	echo "Welcome $i times"
done

for i in {1..100}
do 
	mkdir $i
done


* Login to a remote system
ssh erik
Show rhythynbox running on laptop. Play music
Show tunnelling example (utrace.de)
shutdown the system (with android)


* Show cool examples with mail:
** Send a mail with certain information about the filesystem
** ls | mail -s "Contents of my home dir" caspar.wrede@gmail.com
** Use Cowsay
** ls | cowsay | mail -s "Contents of my home dir" caspar.wrede@gmail.com


